Class MashButtonRangeCommand

Mash a button to fill the bar as much as you can in the time allotted. There is a range of values evenly distributed across the bar. The end result will be a value based on how much of the bar is filled when the Action Command ends.

For attacks such as Huff N. Puff's Wind Breath, the start value should be higher than the end value so filling the bar decreases the damage dealt.
